# VulkanDesktop — test & smoke-run CLI

Full reference: [`Docs/CLI.md`](../../Docs/CLI.md). Implementation: `VulkanDesktop/Util/Util_EngineConfig.cpp`.

**Binary:** `x64\Debug\VulkanDesktop.exe` (after `MSBuild VulkanDesktop.sln /p:Configuration=Debug /p:Platform=x64`).

**Log:** `Logs/engine_runtime_log.txt` (repo root; fresh each run).

---

## Asset root (preferred)

**Agents / CI / odd cwd:** always pass explicit root — do not rely on cwd discovery alone.

```powershell
.\VulkanDesktop.exe --asset-root <repo-root> --no-validation --smoke-seconds 6
```

P0 target: fail fast when `assetRoot` unresolved (`ci-verification_Plan.md`). Until then, explicit `--asset-root` is the contract for automated runs.

---

## When to use which command

| Goal | Command |
|------|---------|
| CLI parses, no GPU | `.\VulkanDesktop.exe --help` |
| Full lifecycle (preferred task close) | **Graceful smoke** below |
| Minimal scene | `--scene Data/Scenes/smoke.json` |
| Scene/manifest/path work | `--scene …` + `--asset-root <repo-root>` |
| CI/agent without validation layers | `--no-validation` |

---

## Graceful smoke (task close)

From `x64\Debug`:

```powershell
Set-Location x64\Debug
.\VulkanDesktop.exe --asset-root <repo-root> --no-validation --smoke-seconds 6
```

Variants: `--scene Data/Scenes/demo.json` · `smoke.json` · `--smoke-frames 2` (fast; both thresholds apply if combined with `--smoke-seconds`).

### Success signals (tail log)

- `[CONFIG] assetRoot=…` under repo
- `[SCENE] LoadSceneResources completed`
- `[APP] Smoke dwell reached` · `[SCENE] UnloadScene` · `[APP] Engine exited run loop normally`
- Exit code **0**; no new `[ERROR]` on init (`--no-validation` OK)

---

## Build (before smoke)

```powershell
& "${env:ProgramFiles(x86)}\Microsoft Visual Studio\Installer\vswhere.exe" -latest -requires Microsoft.Component.MSBuild -find MSBuild\**\Bin\MSBuild.exe
& "<MSBuild.exe>" VulkanDesktop.sln /p:Configuration=Debug /p:Platform=x64 /v:m
```

